%N A167693 Number of reduced words of length n in Coxeter group on 22 generators S_i with relations (S_i)^2 = (S_i S_j)^15 = I.
%C A167693 The initial terms coincide with those of A170741, although the two sequences are eventually different.
%C A167693 Computed with Magma using commands similar to those used to compute A154638.
